{"questionId":"4b6f0a3f","correctAnswer":"5","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Identify coefficients","content":"$x^2-5x-24=0$ has $a=1$, $b=-5$."},{"title":"Apply Vieta&apos;s sum formula","content":"$$\\text{sum of solutions}=\\frac{-b}{a}=\\frac{-(-5)}{1}=5$$<br/>The answer is <strong>5</strong>.","desmosExpressions":["y=x^2-5x-24"]}]}